title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 13 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 13 2022
description:
Malfunctioning cameras hamper subway shooting investigation. Liberals call for more gun laws. NYC Mayor Eric Adams blames rising crime on "historical inequalities." New York Post columnist and author Miranda Devine joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Hunter Biden "Laptop from Hell" and the media's continued effort to ignore this blockbuster story about "the Big Guy" -- who she says she's been told is a focus of the grand jury investigation. Former NFL coach Tony Dungy stands up for fatherhood.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
